  %result = tail call i64 (i64, i32, i8*, i32, ...) @llvm.experimental.patchpoint.i64(i64 9, i32 12, i8* bitcast (i64 (i64, i64)* @foo to i8*), i32 2, i64 %p1, i64 %p2)
